doctitle.textblock: Recordation of Trade Name: ``Superior Seedless Grape Co.''

agency.textblock: U.S. Customs Service, Department of the Treasury.

summary.textblock: On October 27, 1993, a notice of application for the
recordation under section 42 of the Act of July 5, 1946, as
amended (15 U.S.C. 1124), of the trade name ``Superior Seedless
Grape Co.,'' was published in the
The notice advised that before final action was taken on the
application, consideration would be given to any relevant data,
views, or arguments submitted in writing by any person in
opposition to the recordation and received not later than
December 27, 1993. No responses were received in opposition to
the notice. Accordingly, as provided in ยง133.14, Customs
Regulations (19 CFR 133.14), the name ``Superior Seedless Grape
Co.,'' is recorded as the trade name used by Sun World, Inc.,
a corporation organized under the laws of the State of Delaware,
located at P. O. Box 1028, 53-990 Enterprise Way, Coachella,
The trade name is used in connection with table grapes.
